      "description": "We are pleased to present this immaculate specimen, curated for the most discerning collector. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this unit represents the pinnacle of its class. For those who prioritize uncompromising quality and investment-grade preservation, this offering stands as a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine automotive asset.",
      "price": 48900.0,
